315 template <class Base>
316 bool TLoggerWrap<Base>::SendLogMessage(
317  istd::IInformationProvider::InformationCategory category,
318  int id,
319  const QString& message,
320  const QString& messageSource,
321  int flags) const
322 {
323  if (m_logPtr != NULL){
324  QString correctedMessage = message;
325  QString correctedMessageSource = messageSource;
326 
327  DecorateMessage(category, id, flags, correctedMessage, correctedMessageSource);
328 
329  m_logPtr->AddMessage(istd::TSmartPtr<const istd::IInformationProvider>(new ilog::CMessage(category, id, correctedMessage, correctedMessageSource, flags)));
330 
331  return true;
332  }
333 
334  return false;
